\begin_layout Standard
The goal of this note is to show how to translate into a real (or simulated)
 environment the physico-biological setup that the simplest, non-trivial
 Homeostat represents.
 We take as our starting point the classic 2-Unit Homeostat featured in
 Ashby's first experiment (demonstrating 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

The Homeostat as an Adaptor
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

).
\end_layout

